OL,14,Fcriticism from some unionists unhappy
OL,15,Fwith the prospect of returning to the
OL,16,Fpowersharing institutions.JLast week,
OL,17,FSir Jeffrey told MPs that he had been
OL,18,Fpersonally threatened for his efforts
OL,19,Fto negotiate a deal to restore the
OL,20,FAssembly. His party confirmed the
OL,21,Fpolice have been informed.
